      "body": "Soundness review of session 0067 T12 (EntryIdealStratum.lean, 806 LOC): CLEAN. Verified the three flagged risk points are genuinely sound, no vacuity, no off-by-one.\n\n1) fiberRank_baseChange (L122-144): unconditional base-change invariance, NO flatness \u2014 correct; fiber rank = dim_\u03ba(p)(\u03ba(p)\u2297M), proof is cancelBaseChange\u00d72 + Module.finrank_baseChange. Sound.\n2) strataIdeal quasi-coherence map_strataIdeal_basicOpen (L655): denominator-clearing is noetherian-free \u2014 finite subcover from affine quasi-compactness (isCompact.elim_finite_subcover in ChartsCover.exists_finite_charts) + Finset.sup of clearing powers. Sound.\n3) mem_range_stratum\u03b9_iff (L777): support = rank EXACTLY e, not \u2264 e. Reduces to EntryIdeal.entryIdeal_le_prime_iff (entryIdeal \u2264 p \u2194 fiberRank p M = e), both directions proved genuinely (entryIdeal = ideal of 1\u00d71 minors; \u2286 p \u27fa relMatrix \u2261 0 mod p \u27fa fiber has full dim e). No off-by-one/\u2264-vs-= slip. Chart-independence (chartFiberRank_eq, pointRank_eq_chartFiberRank) genuinely established via common-basic-open refinement + fiberRank_of_isLocalizedModule.\n\nSCOPE CAVEAT for downstream (not a bug): stratum/stratum\u03b9/strataData all require hcov : ChartsCover G e, which \u2014 since an e-generator presentation caps fiber rank at e (fiberRank_le) \u2014 forces fiber rank \u2264 e at EVERY point of X. So 'rank-e stratum as closed subscheme of X' is constructed only when e globally bounds fiber rank (i.e. after restricting to the open {rank \u2264 e}, or e maximal). This is faithful to Nitsure's inductive n=0 construction and is an honestly-named Prop hypothesis, not hidden \u2014 but flatLocusStratification_universal (Stage D/E, still 1 deliberate sorry) must discharge ChartsCover for the actual base. Verdict: genuine convergent progress, math-sound substrate.",
